des:
Radio More FM was inaugurated on July 10, 2008, in Santo Cristo, and on December 8, 2010, it opened its studio in the city of Santa Rosa.

The station has cutting-edge technology, studios equipped with digital automation software and state-of-the-art equipment, which guarantee quality in musical performance and precision in commercial broadcasting 24 hours a day.

Our programming is carefully analyzed, developed and designed to ensure high audience ratings, which is already a reality. A young and qualified team creates the basis for the station's interactive, dynamic and objective programming, always in high spirits, cultivating and captivating new listeners every day and maintaining the commitment to return on investment for our advertisers.
